After each personality update, PROMISE composes an integrated regulation instruction by concatenating trait-relevant behavior prompts for all non-neutral traits. When trait recommendations conflict, the system prioritizes emotional safety (Security domain) over stimulation (Arousal domain), consistent with clinical guidance {[}51{]}.

